message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been valued at $120 by you. Considering its quality and unique features, I believe it's a great opportunity for you to experience its benefits. To make this deal even more attractive, I'm offering you the chance to purchase it today for $110. Don't miss out on this exceptional value; it's a rare opportunity to get a top-tier product at an exclusive price. Let me know if you're interested!
